Hi @ankur6ue , @peterjc123 , how to perform visualization on the trained pytorch model on windows. I followed the pytorch faster-rcnn obtained here https://github.com/ruotianluo/pytorch-faster-rcnn to perform visualization on that model, but with the following error on x64 Native Tools Command Prompt for VS2017 and also on Windows 10 Command Prompt.

tensorboard --logdir=tensorboard\vgg16\icdar_train --port=7001
SyntaxError: unexpected character after line continuation character

@ankur6ue , how you perform visualization as the picture showed previously ?
I hope to get some information. Thank you
